  "body": "**NOTE:** _**there is significant difference between ### SHARE and ### INVITE community flows on mobile**_\r\n\r\n**Steps:**\r\n\r\n1. as a mobile (device A) -> create a community that requires approval to join\r\n2. as a mobile (device A) -> add desktop (device B) to contacts\r\n3. as mobile (device A) -> go to community you just created and tap 3 dots -> view profile -> **SHARE** icon \r\n4. as mobile (device A) -> select desktop (device B) to share the community\r\n\r\n**As a result on device B (desktop):**\r\n\r\n- join community button is shown in 1x1 chat \r\n- when clicked Join -> user is joined as follower (can't post messages, can't see channels)\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1431\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-05-07 at 09 38 42\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/117408229-4d8b9000-af18-11eb-9be8-2207856a26b6.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1431\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-05-07 at 09 41 03\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/117408326-72800300-af18-11eb-8383-46d3b2eed1eb.png\">\r\n\r\n![IMG_DFBEB9CB5AC0-1](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/117408407-92172b80-af18-11eb-99aa-d4fd9296bf92.jpeg)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected:**\r\n\r\n1. Request access should be shown instead of join since this community requires approval\r\n2. When user clicks Request approval -> get approval -> he can post messages to any channels, all channels are visible to the user",
